<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
<head>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8"/>
    <title>Java Techie Mail</title>
    <link href="/css/template-style.css" rel="stylesheet" />
</head>

<body>
<table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
    <tr>
        <td align="center" valign="top" bgcolor="#838383"
            style="background-color: #838383;"><br/> <br/>
            <table width="600" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
                <tr>
                    <td valign="top" bgcolor="#d3be6c"
                        style="background-color: #d3be6c; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; color: #000000; padding: 0px 15px 10px 15px;">
                        <br />
                        <div align="center" style="font-size: 32px; color:blue;">
                            <b>Warehouse System</b>
                        </div>
                        <div style="font-size: 18px; color: #555100;">
                            <br/> Hello ${name}<br/>
                        </div>
                        <p>We inform you that the company network password for your account user <b>${userId}</b> will expire in <b>${days}</b> days.</p>
                        <br/>
                        <div align="left">
                            <p><b>Remember to change your password before it expires</b> in order to continue using company services (corporate network access, mail, applications, etc.).</p>
                        </div>
                        <br/>
                        <div>
                            <p>To change your password, wherever you are, follow the instructions in the short guide attached.</p>
                            <br/>
                            <p>The guide will also always be available on the One Click Portal, by typing "Change corporate network password" in the search bar.</p>
                            <span><b>Attention, this link is valid for a period of 15 minutes.</b> Beyond that, you will have to start the procedure again on the <a target="_blank" href="http://localhost:4201/warehouse/dashboard/change/password">Change my password</a> website.</span>
                            <br/>
                            <p>If you need assistance, please use the WAREHOUSE virtual assistant from the intranet or via Teams. If the problem is not resolved, you can contact the Support at the following numbers: 1807695 (from company network) or +39 06 4522 7695 (from external).</p>
                            <br/>
                            <p>Thank you for your confidence.</p>
                            <p>Best regards</p>
                            <br/>
                        </div>
                    </td>
                </tr>
            </table>
            <br/>
        </td>
    </tr>
</table>
</body>
</html>